            <h2>Current Focus</h2>
            <p>Currently, I am focused on sourcing environmentally sustainable products for a company in the UAE. The UAE offers incentives for immigration business purposes to start-ups that provide ecologically sustainable alternatives to single-use plastics. Our goal is to help innovative companies introduce their sustainable products to the UAE and the region through our established network and expertise as local agents.</p>
        </section>
