            <h2>Professional Experience</h2>
            <p>Previously, I founded Razi Law, specializing in property division, divorce, and family law. As an Associate, I provided insightful guidance with practical and focused end-driven advice, fostering inclusive environments where individuals thrive, feel valued, and express their authentic selves. I am recognized for my ability to turn challenges into opportunities with a creative, strategic, and practical approach. My legal expertise includes Indigenous Residential School claims, Criminal Law, Wills and Estates, Immigration, Residential Tenancy Law, and Family Law.</p>
